{"tid":774283,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"條港燦唔讓坐比我公公 我立即拍片放左上微博","createTime":"2018-08-10T08:10:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-10T12:22:21.000Z","uid":1734,"like":5,"dislike":62,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"79f990227cd5d9609c79c66067df2178e03bc2da","tid":774283,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T08:10:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我大陸既公公婆婆落黎玩幾日 咁佢地年紀都比較大 都50幾歲啦 其實行動都唔係幾方便 咁我地坐港鐵 但香港人從來掛住玩手機唔讓坐 咁我公公又好攰 咁見到有個後生仔又大隻又精神 我就叫佢讓坐 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  後生仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  靚仔可唔可以讓一讓比我公公<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  點解要我讓<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你後生又大隻 應該讓下比老人家<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  老鳳？ 唔撚讓 （我即刻燥燥地）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點呀 係唔讓？ <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我即刻拍佢片 放左上微博公審佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人真係無咩同理心 始終我地大陸比較有素質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56a26dc7a731d0393d461d3b983f7f3caf88b544","tid":774283,"uid":6273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T08:12:25.000Z","msg